text: "Falling in Love (Uh-Oh)" is a 1986 song by Miami Sound Machine featuring Gloria Estefan and taken from their 9th studio album Primitive Love. It went to number 22 in Belgium, number 25 in the United States, number 26 in the Netherlands and number 89 in the United Kingdom. It did not chart in Australia or New Zealand. ==Formats and track listings== Category:1986 songs Category:Gloria Estefan songs
title: Falling in Love (Uh-Oh)
